data.description: Immaculately kept full-brick home featuring stunning vaulted ceilings in the main area. This three bedroom, two bath property boasts a large fenced backyard, granite countertops, new HVAC in 2021 and much more. Located in the highly desirable Heathrow neighborhood, this is a "must-see gem!" This home comes with an added bonus - a 6% assumable loan option which does not require the purchaser to pay for an appraisal. Make this incredible property yours!
